{"tid":2006941,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"孫興慜今日完成海軍陸戰隊訓練，157人中排名第一，以滿分結業","createTime":"2020-05-08T06:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T06:24:08.000Z","uid":31744,"like":413,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"c89614a7b07c0a1597d689fa05ad637b3e4b4902","tid":2006941,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"據韓國聯合通訊社消息，孫興慜在今天上午結束了海軍陸戰隊的軍事訓練，在157名參訓人員中，結業排名第一，並獲得了獎項。<br />\n<br />\n孫興慜在3月20日進入濟州西歸浦市的海軍陸戰隊訓練營，進行為期三週的軍事訓練，其中包括心理素質和戰鬥訓練，涵蓋了個人槍支射擊、刺刀、槍支拆卸、個人戰鬥、行軍拉練等多項訓練項目。<br />\n<br />\n在最終的結業測試中，孫興慜在射擊訓練中10次10環，心理能力評估也是獲得滿分，此外在其他項目中都表現得很出色。在每次戰鬥中，他還履行了班長的職責。<br />\n<br />\n一名訓練營的軍官也表示：「孫興慜是一位有禮貌、舉止端莊的學員，雖然他不是海軍陸戰隊隊員，不過我希望他能成為一個越來越強大的球員，永遠銘記在訓練中的不屈不撓的戰鬥精神。」<br />\n<br />\n來源：虎撲體育<br />\n<br />\n-Leo"},{"pid":"2c67367cab9b004f94033d22e479f9dc45c358cd","tid":2006941,"uid":300938,"like":556,"dislike":2,"score":554,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T06:06:47.000Z","msg":"係熱刺食過夜粥係唔同D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb15036e408453797273a36e1c52bdeaa7dec3f","tid":2006941,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EXW4UVKUYAAmKTU?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lih.kg%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEXW4UVKUYAAmKTU%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0OaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=8c3371d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.lih.kg/540/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EXW4UVKUYAAmKTU?format=jpg&amp;name=medium</a><br />\n<br />\n請槍姐<br />\n唔記得交換返頂綠帽"},{"pid":"093132c59989f45c13467d0c3df189c272e2b6f5","tid":2006941,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"造神？"},{"pid":"6893